Class CloneConfirmIterator<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • wblut.external.straightskeleton.CloneConfirmIterator<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Iterator<E>

    public class CloneConfirmIterator<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>
    Part of campskeleton: http://code.google.com/p/campskeleton/ Original Copyright Notice: http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0 An iterator that wraps a set to give an interator that checks for item removal from the original set before returning it. Note that this does not check for addition to the set (you will only get a subset of the objects in the original set, nothing that is added after this iterator is constructed)
    Author:
    twak
